				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Xu%C3%A2n-L%C3%B4i/Di%E1%BB%87p-m%C3%A3-nhi-ph%C3%BA/poem-9s5DpVQjHsixE2k1b-RLdA">Diệp mã nhi phú - 葉馬兒賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Xu%C3%A2n-L%C3%B4i/author-6rhfZvRmtlyU1Z-Y69osfw">Đoàn Xuân Lôi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/%C4%90o%E1%BA%A3n-ca-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-43Lf49JtQxAUhD_uQQ76eA">Đoản ca hành kỳ 2 - 短歌行其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/author-eKAWfrr_7bNBR5FBbe19qg">Tào Tháo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Ng%E1%BA%ABu-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-L1QfrDSXsyRjaRsPd0LCCw">Ngẫu hứng kỳ 4 - 偶興其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/Nh%C3%A0n-t%C3%ACnh-ph%C3%BA/poem-SfJjdY1BShl5c2Q2RpHH7g">Nhàn tình phú - 閑情賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Thi%E1%BB%87n-%C4%90%E1%BB%85/T%E1%BA%A3o-%C4%91%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-quy/poem-xLvjNPr1_m_UK_McsgwiYw">Tảo đương quy - 早當歸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Thi%E1%BB%87n-%C4%90%E1%BB%85/author-igZLqt41xRoFDadZEcE1Gg">Vũ Thiện Đễ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/T%E1%BA%B7ng-%C4%90inh-D%E1%BB%B1c/poem-Z_PpO1_rG-tl9DAKFT4lyw">Tặng Đinh Dực - 贈丁翼</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A7n-Gia/T%E1%BA%B7ng-ph%E1%BB%A5-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-_xsZ8rXc0C1mMyrDhsuQ4A">Tặng phụ thi kỳ 1 - 贈婦詩其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A7n-Gia/author-djGByRNyyXxtcykD8j_JTA">Tần Gia</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bang-B%E1%BA%A3n/Th%E1%BA%A7n-Ph%C3%B9-h%E1%BA%A3i-kh%E1%BA%A9u/poem-m3wKHW20HqOAQRoE9h6AYQ">Thần Phù hải khẩu - 神浮海口</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Bang-B%E1%BA%A3n/author-s5no_WN-Qbyowo0KXT53Zg">Dương Bang Bản</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/Thu%E1%BB%B7-c%E1%BB%91c-d%E1%BA%A1-h%C3%A0nh-k%C3%BD-T%E1%BB%AD-M%E1%BB%B9-Th%C3%A1nh-Du/poem-FFz1vwSnqt3-FS9BXxREFQ">Thuỷ cốc dạ hành ký Tử Mỹ, Thánh Du - 水谷夜行寄子美聖俞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-vpkhTYu5I0Ga1J2slJa8Pw">Trường hận ca - 長恨歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/author-LhlsyQN9Bp8xEaFjAVEqow">Vương Kiều Loan</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
